Chicago Traffic Camera Analytics Pipeline

Overview
Built an end-to-end data analysis pipeline for Chicago traffic datasets.

What I Did
- Wrote SQL queries to filter and join datasets
- Automated reporting in Python
- Visualized trends and comparisons

Tools Used
- SQL
- Python (Pandas, Matplotlib)
- Data Analysis

Outcome
- Identified traffic patterns
- Compared violation trends
- Generated visual reports
